data.description: Welcome to 70 Tashmoo Avenue, located in the heart of Vineyard Haven, This classic home boasts 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms across over 3,200 sq ft of space of living space. Nestled in the perfect in-town Vineyard Haven neighborhood, this residence offers unparalleled convenience. Main Street, Owen Park, the Ferry, Owen Little Way Beach, and the Vineyard Haven Yacht Club are within walking distance. This historic home exudes timeless charm and potential. The property includes a 400 sq ft heated studio. The possibilities are vast. The property sits on a large lot with numerous opportunities, including the potential for subdividing and adding a guest house. Preliminary engineering has already been completed for the subdivision, but town approval is required. Title V inspection has passed and the property is NOT situated in the watershed area. Make your vision a reality with a spacious family retreat or a prime investment opportunity.
